# Committed template. For local overrides use ".env.local" (see env.local.example).
#
# ZATCA signing runs in fcm-server/zatca-service.js (Node). The web/Electron app calls it over HTTP(S).
# If VITE_ZATCA_SERVICE_URL is unset, the client defaults to http://localhost:3002 (same machine only).
#
# Production: deploy the API (Docker: fcm-server/Dockerfile), put HTTPS in front (Nginx/Caddy),
# then set the line below in .env.local and run: npm run build   or   npm run desktop:build
#
# VITE_ZATCA_SERVICE_URL=https://zatca-api.yourdomain.com
# Full VPS steps: fcm-server/DEPLOY.md
